data.description: This is it! Have a beautiful home for the holidays! This charming home has everything you're looking for! Open floor plan, beautiful views, 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and plenty of space for entertaining! The back deck over looks the entire Antelope Valley and provides gorgeous views of the desert sunsets. Your next home is also conveniently located right by the freeway and close to shopping, churches, and schools! I don't want this superb home by you by! Schedule an appointment to view today!
